org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.cassandra

类 CassandraCommitter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.runtime.operators.CheckpointCommitter
      • org.apache.flink.streaming.connectors.cassandra.CassandraCommitter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CassandraCommitter
extends CheckpointCommitter
    CheckpointCommitter that saves information about completed checkpoints within a separate table in a cassandra database.

    Entries are in the form |operator_id | subtask_id | last_completed_checkpoint|

      • lastCommittedCheckpoints

        private final java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Long> lastCommittedCheckpoints
        A cache of the last committed checkpoint ids per subtask index. This is used to avoid redundant round-trips to Cassandra (see isCheckpointCommitted(int, long).
